## 2026-03-28 - Generator auto-run from tokenStore.onChange has no concurrency guard
- Replaced `runningGenerators` Set (which silently skipped concurrent runs) with a per-generator promise-chain mutex (`generatorLocks` Map) that serializes concurrent executions
- Added `withGeneratorLock()` method implementing the promise-chain pattern: each call chains behind the previous for that generator ID, auto-cleans when idle
- Wrapped both auto-run path (`runForSourceToken`) and manual run path (`run()`) with the lock so they don't race each other

